---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="bg-footer-bg border-t border-border-color py-10 px-6 text-text-secondary transition-all duration-300">
	<div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto flex flex-col gap-4">
		<!-- Top Row: Logo & Description -->
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center md:items-start gap-6">
			<div class="flex items-center">
				<img src="/logo.png" alt="MangaK Logo - Kênh review truyện tranh Manga, Manhua, Manhwa" class="h-10 w-auto block" />
			</div>
			<p class="max-w-[500px] text-center md:text-right text-[0.95rem] text-text-muted leading-relaxed font-body">
				Kênh đánh giá, review truyện tranh Manga, Manhua, Manhwa. Nơi kết nối niềm đam mê đọc truyện.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Divider -->
		<hr class="border-0 border-t border-border-color" />

		<!-- Partner Links -->
		<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1 text-[11px] text-text-muted pb-2">
			<a href="https://teamsohoa.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" title="Team Số Hoá">Team Số Hoá</a>
			<span>|</span>
			<a href="https://xuhuong24.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" title="Xu Hướng 24">Xu Hướng 24</a>
			<span>|</span>
			<a href="https://mangak.site" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" title="MangaK - Truyện tranh miễn phí">MangaK - Truyện tranh miễn phí</a>
			<span>|</span>
			<a href="https://khaizinam.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" title="Khaizinam - Blog">Khaizinam - Blog</a>
			<span>|</span>
			<a href="https://www.facebook.com/mangakfreevn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" title="Fanpage Facebook MangaK">Fanpage Facebook</a>
			<span>|</span>
			<a href="/robots.txt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" title="robots.txt">robots.txt</a>
			<span>|</span>
			<a href="/llms.txt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" title="llms.txt dành cho AI">llms.txt</a>
		</div>

		<!-- Bottom Row: Copyright & Disclaimer -->
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-[0.85rem] text-text-muted font-body">
			<p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} MangaK (mangak.io.vn). All rights reserved.</p>
			<p class="text-[0.75rem] max-w-[800px] text-center md:text-right">Tất cả thông tin và đánh giá thuộc bản quyền của MangaK Team.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
